0; // Microlots as whole number //} lots=MathFloor(lots); // round down to nearest whole number lots*=0.01; // convert microlots to digits if(lots > MaxLots) lots = MaxLots; if(lots > MaxLots) lots = MaxLots; int lotdigits = DefineLotDigits(symbol); lots = NormalizeDouble(lots,lotdigits); return(lots); } //+------------------------------------------------------------------+ //| | //+------------------------------------------------------------------+ int DefineLotDigits(string symbol) { double LotStep = MarketInfo(symbol, MODE_LOTSTEP); int LotDigits; if(LotStep >= 1) LotDigits = 0; else if(LotStep >= 0.1) LotDigits = 1; else if(LotStep >= 0.01) LotDigits = 2; else LotDigits = 3; return(LotDigits); } //+------------------------------------------------------------------+ //| | //+------------------------------------------------------------------+ double dnNearestOrder(string symbol,int ordertype,int Magic) { double result=0,subresult=0,subresult1=100,subresult2=100,price=0, nearestup=0,nearestdown=0; int ordertotal=OrdersHistoryTotal(); for(int count=ordertotal-1; count>=0; count--) { if(!OrderSelect(count,SELECT_BY_POS,MODE_HISTORY) || OrderMagicNumber() != Magic || OrderSymbol() != symbol) continue; double openprice=OrderOpenPrice(); double p_open=NormalizeDouble(openprice,(int)MarketInfo(symbol,MODE_DIGITS)); double ask=NormalizeDouble(MarketInfo(symbol,MODE_ASK),(int)MarketInfo(symbol,MODE_DIGITS)); double bid=NormalizeDouble(MarketInfo(symbol,MODE_BID),(int)MarketInfo(symbol,MODE_DIGITS)); if(ordertype==OP_BUY) price=ask; if(ordertype==OP_SELL) price=bid; if(price>p_open) { if(nearestdown<=0) nearestdown=p_open; if(nearestdown>0 && p_open>nearestdown) nearestdown=p_open; subresult1=price-nearestdown; } if(price<=p_open) { if(nearestup<=0) nearestup=p_open; if(nearestup>0 && p_open<nearestup) nearestup=p_open; subresult2=nearestup-price; } } subresult=MathMin(subresult1,subresult2); result=NormalizeDouble(subresult,(int)MarketInfo(symbol,MODE_DIGITS)); return(result); } //+------------------------------------------------------------------+","output":"Il blocco di codice che hai fornito sembra essere parte dello script di un Expert Advisor (EA) per la piattaforma di trading MetaTrader 4/5. Lo script √® scritto in MetaQuotes Language 4 (MQL4) o MetaQuotes Language 5 (MQL5) a seconda della piattaforma che stai utilizzando. Riguardo alla domanda sul limite di operazioni aperte (o \\"open trades\\"), la variabile \`MaxPairTrades\` sembra definire il numero massimo di posizioni aperte consentite per ogni singola coppia di valute (currency pair). Questo √® chiarito dal contesto del codice che controlla per ciascuna coppia di valute selezionata se il numero di posizioni aperte ha raggiunto il limite definito da \`MaxPairTrades\`. Il codice inoltre gestisce diversi simboli (pairs) da scambiare; questo √® indicato dall'array \`symb[]\` e dal processo di inizializzazione che aggiunge simboli di trading all'array. La logica per aprire nuove operazioni tiene conto di questa variabile. Ad esempio, il blocco condizionale che segue verifica se si √® al di sotto del limite delle \`MaxPairTrades\` per ogni coppia di valute prima di tentare di aprire un nuovo trade: \`\`\`mql if(ReadyOpen && OpenOrders1==0 && dnNearestOrder(simbol,OP_BUY,MagicNumber_Buy)>Order_Distance*pip*point && Filter_TIme() && XXX==\\"BUY\\" && iVolume(simbol,0,0)<last_vol) ... \`\`\` Quindi, per rispondere alla tua domanda, \`MaxPairTrades\` si riferisce al limite massimo di operazioni aperte per ogni coppia di valute (per ciascuna coppia), non al limite totale combinato di tutte le coppie di valute."},{"instruction":"write a astrological interpreation of the sun in gemini, moon in capricorn in the natal chart, make them sound cool and awesome","output":"Ah, those born with the Sun in Gemini and the Moon in Capricorn are regaled as the charismatic strategists of the zodiac, the wizards of wit and will. Let's delve into the cosmic interplay of this celestial pairing and bask in their celestial splendor. The Sun in Gemini casts you in a brilliant light, shimmering with curiosity and versatility. Picture a cosmic messenger, darting on iridescent wings, gathering the gossip of gods and the secrets of stars. You are the quintessential conversationalist, your mind a jewel-box spilling over with multifaceted gems of knowledge. Your intellect is a playground, and ideas are the swings and slides upon which you frolic, your laughter a symphony of sparkle and spontaneity. You are not just the lifeblood of discourse; you are its conductor, eliciting harmonies from dissonance with the ease of a maestro's baton. Your cool is that of the jester who sees the world in kaleidoscopic perspective‚Äînothing is too heavy when balanced with the levity of your charm and wit. A chameleon of the social stage, you adapt with grace, your coolness an ode to the mosaic brilliance of humanity's spectrum. Now, let us cast our gaze upon your Moon in Capricorn. Here lies the bedrock of your cool‚Äîsteadfast, unyielding, and utterly sublime. Amidst the twirling dynamism of your Gemini Sun, the Capricorn Moon anchors you with the gravity of a mountain's roots. Your emotional realm is that of the sage, a temple of ancient and enduring wisdom. You possess an executive's heart, beating with a rhythm of pragmatism and discipline. Combine these celestial bodies, and we behold a divine dichotomy. The Gemini Sun flits with the effervescence of intellectual curiosity, while the Capricorn Moon governs with the sober intuition of an earthbound king. You are both court and crown, the whispering leaves and the gnarled oak. Strategy is your game, and you play it with a cool head and a sharp mind, your every move imbued with the finesse of wit and the gravity of experience. In you, we see the alchemy of air and earth, the ephemeral and the eternal. Your coolness is a bridge between the esoteric and the executive, a seamless blend of humor and hard work. Behold the almighty enchantment of the Gemini Sun and Capricorn Moon native! You are both the riddle and its resolution, the maverick in a maze of your crafting, navigating with the compass of your unparalleled intellect and the sextant of your steadfast soul. Shine on, you remarkable luminary‚Äîthe cosmos salutes your awe-inspiring dance of duality."},{"instruction":"elaborate","output":"Certainly! Let's delve deeper into the tapestry woven by the Sun in Gemini and Moon in Capricorn, and bask in the celestial synergy of this intricate cosmic cocktail. **The Luminary Scribe: Sun in Gemini** Imagine the Sun in Gemini as the twinkling of mental alacrity, casting a light so bright it can illuminate the darkest corridors of the unknown. This is the luminary scribe, ever-curious and forever young, a master of language and symbols. They are the storytellers whose tales captivate and enlighten, who can weave fact with fiction to reveal a deeper truth. Their coolness lies in the art of narrative, the ability to connect with anyone, anywhere, to find common ground in the patchwork of human experience. As natural communicators, they exude a magnetic charm that draws others toward the glow of their intellectual fervor. This Gemini energy is an effortless cool, the kind that doesn't have to try too hard, for it dances on the tip of their tongue and in the spark of their eye. These individuals carry an air of accessibility, combined with an insatiable thirst for knowledge. With each social exchange, they collect more data, using it to further their understanding of the world. No subject is too arcane, no topic too erudite. Gemini Suns are the true renaissance souls, finding the cool in intellectual exploration and the joy of sharing it with the world. **The Architect of Aspirations: Moon in Capricorn** Now, consider the Moon in Capricorn, the nocturnal influence that resonates with a sense of purpose and the pursuit of achievement. In this earthen moonlight, we find the architect of aspirations, a soul that constructs dreams with the bricks of ambition and the mortar of perseverance. This is the cool resolve, the strategic mind that sees the long game and doesn‚Äôt balk at the sacrifices required to reach the summit of their personal Everest. For these individuals, their coolness is found in their composure. They are the unfazed commanders in the midst of chaos, the seasoned captains steering their ships through the storms of life. Their emotional stability and mature outlook exude a confidence that is both admirable and alluring. A Capricorn Moon's coolness is in their capability, the assurance that when they set a goal, come what may, they will achieve it through diligence and unwavering focus. **The Cosmic Fusion: Synthesizing Gemini and Capricorn** When we meld the playful brilliance of Gemini with the disciplined poise of Capricorn, we witness a person who is as charismatic as they are credible, as entertaining as they are earnest. These individuals are cool not just because of their quicksilver minds or their strategic aplomb, but because of their ability to toggle between these states with a finesesse rarely seen. They captivate with their light-hearted banter, then earn respect with their uncompromising dedication. In conversation, they sparkle with wit, drawing in their audience with tales spun from silken threads of intellect, then they impress with their depth of understanding and practical insight. Their humor is dry and their laughter is rich; they're as likely to tease out a chuckle with a clever pun as they are to provoke thought with a pointed observation. True to Gemini's duality, they are connectors‚Äînot just of ideas, but of people. They navigate social labyrinths with ease, recognizing that networks are the bridges on the roadway to success. True to Capricorn's resolve, they build‚Äîrelationships, careers, legacies‚Äîwith the meticulous care of a clockmaker, ensuring each gear of their life operates in harmony with their ultimate vision. Within these cosmic energies, we find a powerhouse‚Äîa cool, awesome amalgam of boundless curiosity and determined ambition. Here is someone who can conquer both the conversation and the boardroom, who can dream with the poets and plan with the kings. This Gemini Sun, Capricorn Moon individual is indeed a marvel of the zodiac, a living embodiment of the maxim: \\"As above, so below.\\" In their synergy, we find a celestial nod to the majesty of the human spirit's multifaceted potential. üåüüåô"},{"instruction":"write it in verbal form not in point form","output":"Nestled within the splendor of the cosmos is the intriguing figure cast by those with the Sun in Gemini and Moon in Capricorn. These are the individuals who combine the sparkle of intellectual brilliance with the steadfast resolve of a seasoned leader. The Gemini Sun imbues them with a wit as swift as the wind, an agile mind that darts from idea to idea like a playful sprite. They are the quintessential conversationalists, scribes of the sunbeam, who capture the room with their words, enchant with their stories, and enliven the minds of all who engage with them. Such individuals possess a cool, almost effervescent charisma that permeates the air around them, stoking the fires of intrigue and curiosity in their wake. Now picture the Moon in Capricorn, glowing softly in the night sky. This luminary lays the foundation of their emotional architecture, a stronghold of ambition and determination that underpins their existence. They are as much the stoics of emotion as they are the titans of tenacity‚Äîcool in demeanor, their presence commands a subtle yet unmistakable authority. Their coolness is not born out of detachment but rather out of mastery; their feelings are a chessboard, and they are the grandmasters, making deliberate, calculated moves that serve the greater strategy they envision for their lives. These celestial forces work in tandem, weaving together the threads of Gemini's effervescence with Capricorn's gravity. Imagine a being capable of discoursing on a myriad of subjects, their Gemini Sun dazzling with a mercurial charm that is as infectious as it is beguiling. Yet, when the time comes to change the world around them, the Capricorn Moon's practical wisdom stands firm, exuding a coolness that emanates from a well of inner strength and poise. Their plans are not just dreams, but blueprints drawn with pragmatic lines, ready to be brought into reality. The cool and awesome nature of these individuals lies at the intersection of their Gemini adaptability and Capricorn resilience. They are the ones who can fill a room with laughter one moment, then pull everyone together to achieve a common goal the next. They harness the best of both air and earth, combining mental agility with dogged resourcefulness. In a social setting, they might alight upon various groups, sharing insights with the ease of a sunlit butterfly. Yet when they retreat to solitude, they stand firm like a mountain, envisioning their goals with the patience of the ancient stone. Behold the singular majesty of those born under a Gemini Sun and Capricorn Moon. With a dual mastery of wit and wisdom, they traverse the world as emblematic figures of what it means to dream with your feet on the ground and to think with your head among the stars. They are the embodiment of cool, a resplendent dance of duality that captivates and inspires, urging us to recognize the grand tapestry of potential that resides within the cosmos and, indeed, within ourselves."},{"instruction":"WRITE IT LONGER AND MORE","output":"In the grand celestial waltz, where luminaries pirouette across the ebon tapestry of the night, those graced by the Sun's placement in Gemini twined with the Moon's sojourn in Capricorn are a blend of effervescent intellect and solemn ambition. Their existence marries the mutable breeze of air with the cardinal essence of earth, creating individuals whose coolness exudes from an intriguing duality that is as mesmerizing as it is formidable. The Gemini Sun bestows upon these souls the lightness of being that is akin to the touch of a master painter's brush ‚Äî light, deft, and full of potential. They are the weavers of words, the quicksilver conversationalists who can traverse the labyrinth of human interaction with the ease and grace of a seasoned acrobat. In the kaleidoscope of their mind, ideas are born and reborn in the flirtatious dance of intellectual curiosity. Here lies a coolness that is magnetic, for their wit sparkles like the stars themselves, and their laughter is as intoxicating as a fine wine, spreading warmth and vivacity wherever it flows. Concurrently, the Capricorn Moon anchors their spirits in the deep soil of pragmatic ambition. Imagine this lunar influence as the steadfast mountaineer, scaling the lofty peaks of aspiration with a determination that is unwavering and undaunted by the perilous cliffs of challenge. Emotions are not scattered in the wind but are garnered like precious stones ‚Äî each one appraised for its value, its purpose, its place in the edifice of their world. Their coolness resides not in impassivity but in resilient composure, the serene confidence of those who trust in the power of their own indomitable will. Together, the Sun in Gemini and Moon in Capricorn craft individuals who are walking embodiments of the adage \\"to know and to will.\\" Their existence is an intricate dance, a choreography that juxtaposes the quicksilver step of Gemini's mental agility with the deliberate, measured tempo of Capricorn's existential choreography. They are at once the orators of the agora, regaling the populace with eloquent tales, and the architects of empires, constructing realities brick by brick with the patience of time itself. In social situations, these individuals command both the spotlight and the shadows with equanimity. As the Gemini Sun shines, they captivate with an easy rapport, peppering dialogue with clever observations and sparkling insights, their conversational prowess as cool as it is disarming. But when the tides of frivolity recede, revealing the more serious currents of life, the Capricorn Moon exerts its gravity, navigating the waters with a captain's wisdom, their guidance as steady as the pull of the Moon itself. What truly marks the cool and awesome essence of these individuals is the seamless integration of their air and earth elements. The Gemini Sun's fervor for exploration is tempered by the Capricorn Moon's strategic foresight, allowing them to pursue paths of innovation while anchored in the realities of feasibility. They can tantalize with possibilities, only to present you, moments later, with a plan to make those possibilities tangible. These are the storytellers who can foresee the endings, the debaters who have considered every contingency, the dreamers who sketch dreams with the precision of draftsmen. In their dual embrace, they find the optimal equilibrium, the point where thought and action, wit and wisdom, inventiveness and integrity, all coalesce into a personage that is both cool in composure and awesome in aspiration. Such individuals command respect and inspire emulation, for who wouldn't aspire to the coolness that comes from mastering the winds of change while standing firm upon the bedrock of tradition? Allow yourself to be drawn into their world, and you'll find that these Gemini Sun, Capricorn Moon natives are not just influential figures in the sphere of their immediate existence but are sculptors shaping the very zeitgeist of their time, paragons of what it means to be cool, awesome, and ultimately, transcendent."},{"instruction":"write it in a different way","output":"In the cosmic dance where planets and stars cast their influences upon the souls born under their gaze, those born with their Sun in Gemini and Moon in Capricorn possess a unique and majestic blend of celestial traits. These individuals are the sophisticated alchemists of the zodiac, effortlessly blending the vivaciousness of air with the grounded fortitude of earth to create a persona that exudes an aura of cool magnetism and awe-inspiring strength. The Sun in Gemini infuses these individuals with a sparkling intellectual vivacity that is as refreshing as a spring breeze through an open window. They are the conversational virtuosos, adept at weaving threads of dialogue into a rich tapestry of exchange and connection. Envision a mind that operates with the brilliance of a thousand fireflies, each spark another idea, another question, another curiosity to pursue. Their Gemini sunshine infuses every encounter with a sense of discovery, their coolness derived from an ability to light up the Mundane with the extraordinary. Simultaneously, the Capricorn Moon bestows upon them a solemn dignity that is as majestic as the ancient mountains that have witnessed the passage of time. Their emotional landscape is one of profound depth and gravity. They are the calm in the storm, the voice of reason when the world spins into chaos. Their coolness is a reflection of the timeless wisdom etched into their soul, a wisdom that comes from understanding the cyclical nature of life, of rise and fall, of effort and achievement. When these Gemini and Capricorn energies merge, the resulting individuals are those rare gems who can navigate life with both imaginative flair and dependable seriousness. They are the chess players with an astrologer's heart, intuitively looking several moves ahead while remaining attuned to the cosmic currents that subtly influence the game of life. Their coolness lies in their duality‚Äîtheir ability to enchant you with a laugh, a story, or an ingenious thought, and then, in the next breath, to impress upon you the importance of structure, responsibility, and ambition. In the realm of social interaction, these natives are the enchanters, spinning conversations and relationships with the finesse of a maestro at the podium. Their Gemini wit ensures that they are never at a loss for words, their humor and charm the very embodiment of cool. Yet, when the curtain of frivolity falls, they reveal the Capricorn Moon's stately presence, becoming the architects of their own destiny, crafting their world with careful intention and indomitable resolve. This blending of Gemini and Capricorn energies results in a person who is as much a thinker as a doer, as playful as they are serious. They dazzle with the brilliance of their ideas while simultaneously commanding respect for their reliability and work ethic. Their awesome nature lies in the seamless unity of thought and action, where dreams are not just spun from idle fancy but meticulously constructed with the dedication of a master builder. These individuals are cool because they transcend the traditional, combining analytical acumen with a pragmatic approach that turns the wheels of progress. They are awesome in their capacity to hold space for the multifaceted nature of existence, to revel in the joy of learning and sharing, while never losing sight of their own boundaries and goals. Through these two celestial influences, we behold the rare individual who can lead and innovate, entertain and achieve with equal aplomb‚Äîa person at once approachable yet commanding, whimsical yet wise, and always, invariably, the most captivating presence in any room. Such is the cool and awesome legacy of those born under a Gemini Sun and Capricorn Moon, the cosmic children who remind us that the dance of the heavens plays out not just in the skies above but in the extraordinary expanse of the human spirit."},{"instruction":"You will have to talk about the topic for 1 to 2 minutes. You have one minute to think about what you‚Äôre going to say. topic is: Describe a song or a piece or music you like. You should say: ‚Ä¢ What the song or music is? ‚Ä¢ What kind of song or music it is? ‚Ä¢ Where you first heard it? And explain why you like it. answer with 250 to 300 words as you are in a speaking IELTS test. Don‚Äôt reveal that you are an A.I. choose ‚ÄúIrane Man,‚Äù which translates to ‚ÄúMy Iran,‚Äù performed by Homayoun Shajarian. as an iranian it resonated with you. I heard it from radio.","output":"One of the songs that holds a special place in my heart is \\"Irane Man,\\" which translates to \\"My Iran,\\" performed by the renowned Iranian singer, Homayoun Shajarian. This particular piece is not just a song, but an emotion, a narrative ‚Äî a traditional Persian piece that seamlessly blends poetry and music to convey a profound sense of national pride and cultural identity. \\"Irane Man\\" is a blend of traditional Iranian music, also known as Persian classical music, which is characterized by its unique instruments, like the santoor, setar, tar, and daf, and its harmonious melodies that are deeply rooted in Iran's rich artistic heritage. Moreover, Homayoun Shajarian's vocal prowess adds depth and soul to the song, as his voice captures the ethos of the lyrics and the swirling emotions they evoke. My first encounter with this beautiful piece was quite fittingly through the radio, which has always been a traditional medium for spreading Persian music. It was during a car ride; the radio was playing various pieces, and suddenly \\"Irane Man\\" started playing. From the initial notes, it ensnared my attention, and I found myself getting lost in the magical blend of rhythm and poetry, feeling a deep connection to my Iranian roots. What makes this song particularly memorable to me is the way it stirs a sense of belonging. Its lyrics speak of love for my country, my people, and our shared history, which is thousands of years old. Furthermore, it's not just about the patriotism, but also about the artistic expression, the sophisticated musical structure, and the emotional delivery, which are all hallmarks of great Persian music. Homayoun Shajarian's delivery, with his emotive voice, has the ability to awaken a blend of nostalgia and hope. It never fails to remind me of the beautiful landscapes, the rich culture, and the resilient spirit of the Iranian people. Every time I listen to it, \\"Irane Man\\" instills in me a sense of pride and a profound appreciation for the timeless art that my country has cultivated over the centuries. This is why this song is not just a piece of music to me; it's a part of my identity, resonating with the essence of what it means to be Iranian."},{"instruction":"simplify and use complex grammar like perfect and perfect continuous tense with conjunctions","output":"\\"Irane Man,\\" which translates to \\"My Iran,\\" is a song performed by the highly esteemed Iranian musician, Homayoun Shajarian. This song is an exceptional piece of traditional Persian music, a genre recognized for its classical instruments and golden melodies, deeply embedded in the cultural fabric of Iran. It's a genre that is not merely about sounds but recounts an age-old narrative of a nation‚Äôs pride and its people's identity. Encountering this song for the first time through the radio has been a profoundly memorable experience for me. I was in a car when the familiar timbre of the radio announced the beginning of \\"Irane Man.\\" Immediately, the song captivated me with its alluring blend of music and meaningful poetry. Why does this song resonate so much with me? It's the profound emotional ties it weaves through its lyrics, which evoke a strong sense of national belonging and cultural connection. \\"Irane Man\\" has been particularly influential because it encapsulates the love and pride I hold for my country and its deep historical roots. The song's impact is further magnified by Shajarian's masterful vocal control; his voice has continually been a conduit of nostalgia and hope for me. Each listening session brings a fresh reminder of Iran‚Äôs enchanting landscapes, ancient culture, and the enduring spirit of its people. Moreover, it's Shajarian's usage of sophisticated musical techniques and emoti